<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Sellers - DomaHub</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="./css/min/main_sellers.min.css" />
    <%- include("../templates/head_links"); %>
  </head>

<body>

  <%- include("../templates/navbar", {user: user}); %>

  <section id="sellers-img" class="section is-large">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="column">
        <div class="content">
          <h1 class="title is-2 is-white">
            Your domains are valuable assets, <br />
            treat them like they are.
          </h1>
          <h2 class="subtitle is-4 is-white">
            Generate revenue by listing on DomaHub
          </h2>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section is-medium">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-10-tablet is-offset-1-tablet is-10-mobile is-offset-1-mobile">
          <h1 class="is-bold margin-bottom-25">Find out how much you can make with DomaHub.</h1>
          <div class="columns">
            <div class="column is-3 flex-column-center">
              <label class="label">Number of Domains</label>
              <p class="control">
                <input id="num-domains-value" class="input earnings-input" type="number" value="1" min="1" placeholder="Enter a number"/>
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="column is-2 flex-column-center">
              <label class="label">Rate</label>
              <p class="control">
                <span class="select is-fullwidth">
                  <select id="time-value" class="earnings-input">
                    <option value="30">Daily</option>
                    <option value="4">Weekly</option>
                    <option value="1">Monthly</option>
                  </select>
                </span>
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="column is-3 flex-column-center">
              <label class="label">Price</label>
              <p class="control has-icon">
                <input id="price-value" class="input earnings-input" type="number" value="1" min="1" placeholder="Enter a number"/>
                <i class="fa fa-dollar"></i>
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="column is-4">
              <div class="box is-primary has-text-centered">
                <h2 id="earnings-potential" class="is-white is-bold">$ 0</h2>
                <p class="is-white">
                  Per Month
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section is-medium">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="title has-text-centered is-2 has-style-underline margin-bottom-75">
        How to List on DomaHub.
      </h1>
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-offset-1">
          <h2 class="is-bold">1. Signing Up</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-5 is-offset-1">
          <div class="content">
            <span class="icon is-large is-primary margin-bottom-10">
              <i class="fa fa-user-circle-o"></i>
            </span>
            <h3 class="is-bold is-blacklight">Create a DomaHub account</h3>
            <p>
              Creating an account with us is completely free.
              <a class="is-accent" href="/signup" title="Sign Up">Sign up</a>
              using a valid email address and check your email afterwards
              to verify your account. Only users with a DomaHub account can
              create listings with us.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column is-5">
          <div class="content">
            <span class="icon is-large is-primary margin-bottom-10">
              <i class="fa fa-credit-card"></i>
            </span>
            <h3 class="is-bold is-blacklight">Link a Bank Account</h3>
            <p>
              In order to receive and make payments, you must link a bank account
              to your DomaHub account. We make sure your information is secure.
              Payout usually takes a few business days.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-offset-1">
          <h2 class="is-bold">2. Creating Listings</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-5 is-offset-1">
          <div class="content">
            <figure class="image left-aligned is-48x48">
              <img src="/images/lib/material/website.svg" alt="Listing">
            </figure>
            <h3 class="is-bold is-blacklight">List Your Domain(s)</h3>
            <p>
              <a class="is-accent" href="/listings/create" title="Create Listing">Create a listing</a>
              for your domain name(s). You may create listings for multiple domain names simultaneously.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column is-5">
          <div class="content">
            <figure class="image left-aligned is-48x48">
              <img src="/images/lib/material/palette.svg" alt="Listing">
            </figure>
            <h3 class="is-bold is-blacklight">Personalize Your Listings</h3>
            <p>
              All listings can have the following properties: a text description, a
              background header image, a category, and of course price. You have the option to customize
              any of those properties in <a class="is-accent" href="/profile/mylistings" title="My Listings">your listings page.</a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-offset-1">
          <h2 class="is-bold">3. Verifying Your Domains</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-5 is-offset-1">
          <div class="content">
            <figure class="image left-aligned is-48x48">
              <img src="/images/lib/material/dns.svg" alt="Listing">
            </figure>
            <h3 class="is-bold is-blacklight">Redirect Your DNS A Records</h3>
            <p>
              You must
              <a class="is-accent" href="/faq#verifying" title="Point your DNS">point your DNS A Records</a>
              to DomaHub servers for each domain listing. This step is necessary to verify that you are the
              owner of this domain. You may verify a domain in your <a class="is-accent" href="/profile/mylistings" title="My Listings">
              My Listings</a> page.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

